shows.title: Dissonance
shows.plot_overview: Colt Bishop, a down-and-out musician in Albuquerque, finds himself tangled in the world of meth after coming across a recipe that promises massive profits. With the guidance of Badger and Skinny Pete, Colt gets into the game, cooking and dealing to make quick cash. But with his newfound business attracting attention, Colt must navigate the dangers of the criminal world while trying to stay under the radar. As he gets deeper, the line between survival and self-destruction starts to blur.

shows.title: Before the End
shows.plot_overview: As a long-standing bar prepares to close, owner Hung and his young staff member Yip set out to return unclaimed bottles of wine to their owners. Through these encounters, Yip learns the deep connections between the wines and their stories, gaining insight into Hung’s philosophy. Alongside veteran bartender Bill, passionate mixologist Grace, and singer Adam, they create lasting memories for their customers in the bar’s final days.

shows.title: Você Me Vira a Cabeça
shows.plot_overview: After a video of her singing goes viral on the internet, a trans woman's life is transformed, and as she rises in the music world, trying to follow her dream, her relationship and friendships are put to the test.

shows.title: Digimon Beatbreak
shows.plot_overview: Tomoro Tenma lives in a world where human thoughts and emotions, known as e-Pulse, power AI devices called Sapotama. But when Digimon begin materializing from Sapotama and feeding on e-Pulse, society begins to fracture. After Gekkomon appears from his device, Tomoro joins Glowing Dawn, a secret team investigating rogue Digimon and the dark truth of a system both fueled and corrupted by emotion.

shows.title: Monster: The Ed Gein Story
shows.plot_overview: The shocking true-life tale of Ed Gein, the infamous murderer and grave robber who inspired many of Hollywood's most iconic on-screen killers.
